  "title": "Cafe Supervisor | CSOCC02",
  "description": "<p>Cafe Supervisor | CSOCC02<br />This is for one of our client in the F&B Industry<br /></p><p><strong>Locations:</strong><br />Orchard Area (Mall Hours 10am-10pm)<br /></p><p><strong>Work Timings:</strong><br />Work Days: Mon - Sun (Including Sat, Sun & PH)<br />5 Days Work (44 hours per week)<br /></p><p><strong>Compensation:</strong><br />Salary Range: $2,470-$2,950</p><p><br /><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for smooth daily operations in café</li><li>Supervise in compliance with the Company’s Standard Operating Procedures (SOP)</li><li>Assist in overseeing the outlet operations, ensuring operations are running smoothly & efficiently</li><li>Preparation of high quality beverages according to menu</li><li>Light kitchen duties and preparation work</li><li>Provide good customer service</li><li>Basic housekeeping</li><li>Passion for service and F&B industry</li><li>Positive work attitude and a team player</li></ul><p><br />Interested applicants, please click \"<strong>APPLY NOW</strong>\"<br /><br />We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us collecting, using, retaining, and disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.<br /><br /><strong>Joselito</strong> | EA Reg No: R25126580</p>",
